USE hahn; PRAGMA DisableAnsiInForEmptyOrNullableItemsCollections;

$ssku_msku_mapping = (
    SELECT
        IF(
            m.approved_sku_mapping_id > 0,
            m.approved_sku_mapping_id,
            ofs.approved_sku_mapping_id
        ) AS msku,
        ofs.supplier_id as supplier_id,
        s.real_supplier_id || '.' || ofs.shop_sku AS ssku,
        ofs.shop_sku as shop_sku
    FROM `/home/market/production/mbo/stat/mboc_offers/latest`  with inline AS ofs
        JOIN `/home/market/production/mbi/dictionaries/partner_biz_snapshot/latest`  with inline AS s
            ON s.id = ofs.supplier_id
        LEFT JOIN `/home/market/production/mbo/mboc/offer-mapping`  with inline AS m
            ON ofs.shop_sku = m.shop_sku and ofs.business_id = m.business_id
    WHERE s.is_fullfilment = 1 and s.real_supplier_id IS NOT NULL and s.real_supplier_id != '' and (m.approved_sku_mapping_id > 0 OR ofs.approved_sku_mapping_id > 0)
);

SELECT
    m.ssku                  AS ssku,
    m.msku                  AS msku,
    m.supplier_id           AS supplier_id,
    ss.status               AS status
FROM $ssku_msku_mapping AS m
         LEFT JOIN `/home/market/production/deepmind/dictionaries/ssku_status/latest`  with inline AS ss
                   ON ss.shop_sku = m.ssku
